        # Cookbook
        Most cookbooks provide recipes, and the occasional cookbook provides calorie count as well, but it is always **beneficial** to know about the **issues** that **certain ingredients** in a recipe can cause.
        Apart from **celebrating the recipes**, the main aim of creating a cookbook which contains several recipes from around the globe, was to **educate people** on **methylmercury poisoning.** We believe that this would **encourage people** to know more about the issue since it affects their favorite recipes.
