        # Game

        **Taxonomy** is a method of classification of organisms based on their **biological ancestry**. It is also an essential knowledge for all **aspiring biologists**.
        In order to teach children about the **different kingdoms, species** etc, we have designed a game which added a twist to the Tower of Hanoi. We hope that children would enjoy this **unison of mathematics and biology.**

